      },
      {
        "step_no": 3,
        "text": "Add chicken stock and bring to a gentle simmer. Add galangal slices, lemongrass pieces, and torn kaffir lime leaves; simmer gently to infuse aromatics.",
        "time_min": 6
      },
      {
        "step_no": 4,
        "text": "Pour in coconut milk, stir to combine, and return to a gentle simmer. Do not boil vigorously to prevent coconut milk separation.",
        "time_min": 3
      },
      {
        "step_no": 5,
        "text": "Add chicken pieces and mushrooms to the simmering coconut broth; poach gently until chicken is cooked through and mushrooms are tender.",
        "time_min": 7
      },
      {
        "step_no": 6,
        "text": "Season the soup with fish sauce, palm sugar, and fresh lime juice; taste and adjust balance of salty, sweet and sour. Add smashed chiles to reach desired heat.",
        "time_min": 4
      },
